result.title: Attempting RUSSIAN PIPING TIPS using Italian Meringue Buttercream!
result.description:
Italian Meringue VS American Buttercream, I've hacked the perfect recipe!

This week I'm showing how to use Russian piping tips to make beautiful flowers on cupcakes using Italian meringue buttercream. Usually I use American buttercream also known as frosting to pipe Russian piping tip flowers. this Italian meringue buttercream recipe is so silky and light and fluffy making it perfect for cupcakes. But for these tips you need a little bit more structure to your icing. I'm going to show you how I hacked the perfect recipe for Russian piping tips and how to use these texts to make perfect flowers on your cupcakes for your birthday's weddings bridal showers or baby showers. They're simple easy fast and beautiful!
